metadata.name: Begin
metadata.description:
Life is just a shadow! We should move on and go ahead and enjoy life! Begin your life with hope and full of positive energy. 

I took this photograph using my phone camera and edited using Snapseed and mobile Lightroom.

Artist - Tulsi Shankar Kumbhar 
 
Dimension - 4080×3060  

Camera - Samsung Galaxy M33 5G  

Model - SM-M336BU/DS  

dpi - 300  

Date and Time - 9th December 2022, 12:37 PM IST   UTC+5:30
